messageBody:
Enter your vote today! A new poll has been created for the
junit group:

Does the following sound like it is on
topic and should be posted to the list?

"This is the very first book to be
published on JDO, the new
Java object persistence standard that
was adopted by the Java Community
Process in March."

o This is On Topic let it be posted
o This if Off Topic do not let it be posted


To vote, please visit the following web page:

http://groups.yahoo.com/group/junit/surveys?id=973888

Note: Please do not reply to this message. Poll votes are
not collected via email. To vote, you must go to the Yahoo! Groups
web site listed above.

Thanks!
